\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/oneplus-10-pro-b-15.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=310\u0026amp;h=220\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/oneplus-10-pro-b-15.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=310\u0026amp;h=220\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/oneplus-10-pro-b-15.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/oneplus-10-pro-b-15.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/oneplus-10-pro-b-15.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/oneplus-10-pro-b-15.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\u003cimg width=\"2400\" height=\"1600\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"A OnePlus 10 Pro smartphone displaying the list of installed apps.\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/oneplus-10-pro-b-15.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/oneplus-10-pro-b-15.jpg\"/\u003e \u003c/picture\u003e \u003c/figure\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003c/a\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-field=\"label\"\u003eRelated\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003ch5\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.androidpolice.com/best-email-apps-for-android/\" title=\"8 best email apps for Android\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e 8 best email apps for Android \u003c/a\u003e \u003c/h5\u003e\u003cp\u003eIf you\u0026#39;re tired of Gmail, there are plenty of other great options available\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"things-to-know-before-starting-the-process\"\u003e Things to know before starting the process \u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eYou can increase the font size for the emails you write from two places. The first focuses on increasing the size of the text within your email. This means changing the font size every time you write an email. The second is to increase the size through Gmail\u0026#39;s settings to get the same font size every time you write.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe four size options are small, normal, large, or huge. The default setting for emails is normal.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"how-to-increase-the-font-size-of-outgoing-emails\"\u003e How to increase the font size of outgoing emails \u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eGmail offers an option to increase the font size of your text every time you write an email. This can be helpful if you temporarily want to see what you\u0026#39;re writing in a larger text. This could also be helpful when you want to emphasize the content of your email, as increasing the size of keywords draws the reader\u0026#39;s eye to it.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch3 id=\"increase-the-font-size-on-your-computer\"\u003e Increase the font size on your computer \u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003col\u003e\u003cli\u003e Open \u003cstrong\u003eGmail\u003c/strong\u003e. \u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e Click \u003cstrong\u003eCompose\u003c/strong\u003e, located in the upper-left corner of the screen, underneath the Gmail logo. \u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e Open formatting options (\u003cstrong\u003eA\u003c/strong\u003e).\u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gmail-formatting-options.jpg\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gmail-formatting-options.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gmail-formatting-options.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gmail-formatting-options.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gmail-formatting-options.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gmail-formatting-options.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gmail-formatting-options.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gmail-formatting-options.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gmail-formatting-options.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\u003cimg width=\"10885\" height=\"6145\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"text formatting section on gmail\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gmail-formatting-options.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gmail-formatting-options.jpg\"/\u003e \u003c/picture\u003e \u003c/figure\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e Click the \u003cstrong\u003eSize\u003c/strong\u003e option (TT). \u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e Pick from the four size options.\u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gmail-size-options.jpg\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gmail-size-options.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gmail-size-options.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gmail-size-options.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gmail-size-options.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gmail-size-options.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gmail-size-options.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gmail-size-options.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gmail-size-options.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\u003cimg width=\"10885\" height=\"6229\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"text size options on gmail\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gmail-size-options.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gmail-size-options.jpg\"/\u003e \u003c/picture\u003e \u003c/figure\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003c/li\u003e \u003c/ol\u003e\n\n\u003ch3 id=\"increase-the-font-size-on-your-device\"\u003e Increase the font size on your device \u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe following example is specific to Android users. However, iOS users can follow along.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\u003col\u003e\u003cli\u003e Open \u003cstrong\u003eSettings\u003c/strong\u003e. \u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e Search for\u003cstrong\u003e font size\u003c/strong\u003e in Search settings. \u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e Move the \u003cstrong\u003eslider\u003c/strong\u003e to the left to increase the size. \u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e Open the \u003cstrong\u003eGmail app\u003c/strong\u003e. \u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e Tap \u003cstrong\u003eCompose. \u003c/strong\u003e \u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e Write your text in the body. It should appear larger. \u003c/li\u003e \u003c/ol\u003e\n\u003cdiv id=\"custom_block_12\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eA preview of the font appears after changing the size by moving the slider. To change the size, press \n\u003cstrong\u003eReset settings\u003c/strong\u003e\n. This resets the size to the device\u0026#39;s original settings, allowing you to adjust to your liking.\u003c/p\u003e\n \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"how-to-increase-the-default-font-size\"\u003e How to increase the default font size \u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIf you like to write emails in large or huge text (the two sizes larger than Gmail\u0026#39;s default normal), make the change in your settings. You won\u0026#39;t have to increase the font size of your text every time you write an email. You can follow the same steps to make the font size smaller.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\u003col\u003e\u003cli\u003e Open \u003cstrong\u003eGmail\u003c/strong\u003e on your computer. \u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e Click \u003cstrong\u003eSettings\u003c/strong\u003e.\u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gmail-settings-1.jpg\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gmail-settings-1.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gmail-settings-1.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gmail-settings-1.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gmail-settings-1.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gmail-settings-1.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gmail-settings-1.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gmail-settings-1.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gmail-settings-1.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\u003cimg width=\"10885\" height=\"4446\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"settings icon on gmail \" data-img-url=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gmail-settings-1.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gmail-settings-1.jpg\"/\u003e \u003c/picture\u003e \u003c/figure\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e Select \u003cstrong\u003eSee all settings\u003c/strong\u003e.\u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gmail-see-all-settings.png\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gmail-see-all-settings.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gmail-see-all-settings.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gmail-see-all-settings.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gmail-see-all-settings.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gmail-see-all-settings.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gmail-see-all-settings.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gmail-see-all-settings.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gmail-see-all-settings.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\u003cimg width=\"10885\" height=\"4127\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"gmail settings button\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gmail-see-all-settings.png\" src=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gmail-see-all-settings.png\"/\u003e \u003c/picture\u003e \u003c/figure\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e Go to the \u003cstrong\u003eDefault text style\u003c/strong\u003e section (under the General tab). \u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e Select the \u003cstrong\u003eSize option\u003c/strong\u003e (TT). You\u0026#39;ll see a sample of the text in the display box.\u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gmail-size-options-1.jpg\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gmail-size-options-1.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gmail-size-options-1.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gmail-size-options-1.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gmail-size-options-1.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gmail-size-options-1.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gmail-size-options-1.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gmail-size-options-1.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gmail-size-options-1.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\u003cimg width=\"10885\" height=\"6560\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"default size options in gmail settings\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gmail-size-options-1.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gmail-size-options-1.jpg\"/\u003e \u003c/picture\u003e \u003c/figure\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e Scroll down and click \u003cstrong\u003eSave changes\u003c/strong\u003e.\u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gmail-settings-save-changes.jpg\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gmail-settings-save-changes.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gmail-settings-save-changes.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gmail-settings-save-changes.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gmail-settings-save-changes.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gmail-settings-save-changes.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gmail-settings-save-changes.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gmail-settings-save-changes.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gmail-settings-save-changes.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\u003cimg width=\"10885\" height=\"6131\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"save changes button in gmail settings\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gmail-settings-save-changes.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gmail-settings-save-changes.jpg\"/\u003e \u003c/picture\u003e \u003c/figure\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003c/li\u003e \u003c/ol\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eTo reverse any changes when writing an email. Open the toolbar, go to \u003cstrong\u003eMore formatting options\u003c/strong\u003e, and select \u003cstrong\u003eRemove formatting\u003c/strong\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eIf these changes don\u0026#39;t apply, go to Settings and double-check your options. Make sure to save the changes. You can also clear your browser\u0026#39;s cache and cookies.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"increase-the-font-size-of-incoming-emails\"\u003e Increase the font size of incoming emails \u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eYou can view your incoming emails in a larger text in several ways. For one, press \u003cstrong\u003eControl\u003c/strong\u003e and the \u003cstrong\u003ePlus key\u003c/strong\u003e (\u003cstrong\u003e+\u003c/strong\u003e) to increase the text. Use the keyboard shortcut \u003cstrong\u003eControl + 0\u003c/strong\u003e to reset your screen. You can also go into your browser settings to increase the text size.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch3 id=\"increase-the-font-size-on-google-chrome-on-your-computer\"\u003e Increase the font size on Google Chrome on your computer \u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eGoogle Chrome allows you to change the text size for one web page or all the web pages you view. To increase the size of Gmail, follow these steps:\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003col\u003e\u003cli\u003e Open a \u003cstrong\u003eChrome\u003c/strong\u003e browser. \u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e Go to your Gmail account. \u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e Click \u003cstrong\u003eMore\u003c/strong\u003e (the three dots in the upper-right corner). \u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e Press \u003cstrong\u003e+\u003c/strong\u003e to zoom in. \u003c/li\u003e \u003c/ol\u003e\n\n\u003ch3 id=\"increase-the-font-size-on-google-chrome-through-your-phone\"\u003e Increase the font size on Google Chrome through your phone \u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe following example uses an Android phone. iOS users can follow along.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003col\u003e\u003cli\u003e Open \u003cstrong\u003eChrome\u003c/strong\u003e. \u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e Go to \u003cstrong\u003eGmail\u003c/strong\u003e. \u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e Click \u003cstrong\u003eMore\u003c/strong\u003e. \u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e Scroll down to \u003cstrong\u003eZoom\u003c/strong\u003e. \u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e Move the slider to increase the font size. Whatever you choose for this site doesn\u0026#39;t affect how you see other pages. \u003c/li\u003e \u003c/ol\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"going-beyond-the-basics-to-increase-font-size\"\u003e Going beyond the basics to increase font size \u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIncreasing font sizes in Gmail has limitations. While these methods increase the font size, the screen\u0026#39;s proportion could be thrown off, making navigating emails difficult. If you\u0026#39;re in this situation, try different Chrome extensions. Alternatively, import your Gmail \u003ca href=\"https://www.androidpolice.com/transfer-emails-gmail-accounts/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eto a different email provider\u003c/a\u003e that offers settings you like.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n    \n        \n\n    \n\n        \n\n\n                \n        \n        \n\n\n        \n\n\n\n\n\n                    \n        \n    \u003c/article\u003e\n\n    \n            \n        \u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
